controller

Class Controller

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.Controller

  • public class Controller
extends java.lang.Object
    The controller class will let you manipulate Data from the class in the model package and the classes from the view Package to create objects. The controller will also populate the Panes in the View with information from model package.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Caio Eugenio
